Station Update - Martin Place

From 17 November 2021 until 15 December 2021, escalator maintenance will be taking place at Martin Place station. Please take care around the work area, follow directional signage at the station and speak to station staff if you require assistance.
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train
Station Update - Sydenham

Platforms 4, 5 & 6 upgrade works. A new Metro concourse is being constructed on the northern end of Sydenham Station. While the concourse is being installed, please board and alight from the first 5 carriages of the train on platforms 4 & 6 and the last 6 carriages of the train on platform 5. If you need help, please ask staff at the station. For more information on these upgrades, please see sydneymetro.info
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train
Station Update - Tempe

The stairs from Richardsons Crescent to concourse will be closed for maintenance work until November 2021. Access to platforms 2 and 3 will now be via platform 1 side entrance (off carpark on Richardsons Crescent). Entrance from Griffiths St will not be affected.
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train
Station Update - Canterbury

There is no toilet access at Canterbury station until 6 December due to construction works.
Please use public toilets located outside the station.
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train
Station Update - Bexley North, Redfern
Due to station redevelopment work some platforms have reduced capacity. Please avoid standing in front of construction zones and remain behind the yellow line on the platform
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train
Station Update - Central

There are changes happening at Central Station due to Sydney Metro construction works. Access to certain areas of the station and platforms may mean using different stairs, escalators and lifts. Please follow the signs and staff directions. If you need assistance, see station staff. For detailed information please visit https://transportnsw.info/alerts/details#/6063489
https://transportnsw.info/alerts#/train

Please check station information screens and listen to announcements for updates

Please follow the signs and staff directions.

If you need assistance, see station staff.

To access platforms 4 – 23 use the Suburban Tunnel or the Northern Concourse.

Platform re-levelling and re-tiling works are being undertaken during rail shutdown weekends.

For your safety, please move carefully along the platform and follow directions from staff.

∙ From 9.45pm until 1.30am, buses replace trains between Cabramatta and Granville.
∙ Trains run to a changed timetable and stopping pattern between Leppington and Olympic Park via Regents Park, and between Richmond and Olympic Park.
∙ Change at Granville or Cabramatta for buses to Merrylands, Guildford, Yennora, Fairfield and Canley Vale. Change trains at Lidcombe to continue your journey towards Leppington or Richmond.
∙ Plan your trip before you travel for up-to-date real time information.

Bus routes

4T2: Cabramatta, all stations to Granville and return
5T2: Cabramatta, Canley Vale, Fairfield, then express to Granville and return
14T2: Merrylands, then Granville and return
